LBMA-Statistics

Web data extraction from Statistics of the London Bullion Market (London Gold Fixing, London Silver Fixing).

See http://www.lbma.org.uk/pages/index.cfm?page_id=48 for details on London Bullion Market and available Statistics.

Information returned by this module is governed by LBMA's terms and conditions.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc LBMA::Statistics

Have a look at the examples directory, too.

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=LBMA-Statistics

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/LBMA-Statistics

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/LBMA-Statistics

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/LBMA-Statistics/


